  7. [38;5;10mvalidate_letter[0m — provenance verification against [38;5;10mvalid_fact_ids[0m, paraphrase-drift check, DynamoDB status update with [38;5;10mDecimal[0m for the validation rate[0m[0m
- Full pipeline assembly ([38;5;10mprocess_pa_request[0m) with progress prints and a short-circuit when required criteria are unmet[0m[0m
